title: Spyder Auto Installation: Hyundai Genesis Coupe Halo Projector Headlights
description:
This video demonstrates how to install a set of Spyder custom aftermarket headlamps for the popular 2-door Hyundai Genesis Coupe. Follow along as we go through the installation, one step at a time.

Tools Required:
10mm Socket & Ratchet
Phillips Head Screwdriver
Tools Suggested:
Painters Tape/Masking Tape, to protect the car's finish while working.
tags: Spyder Headlights, projector lights, Hyundai Genesis, how to install, spyder lights
